node.text:
Ferguson has been so bright-eyed and chipper these past few days! He’s still very much a waterboy (check the dribble on his chin) but has been eating better & is more active than we’ve ever seen him. Lil dude is really hanging in there. 💕

Also, Ferg is the newest @orphankittenclub trading card!! Check my stories or head to our rescue’s page to find out how you can get one.

node.text:
Hannah recently reminded me that I’ve now been fostering for over 5 years!!! How crazy is that? That’s hundreds of lives that I’ve helped save. Being able to give and nurture on a daily basis has been one of the most fulfilling experiences I’ve ever had. It definitely ain’t all glitz & glamor, but at least even their little butts are cute. 🥰

📸: @kittenxlady
